<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-504] Servers must be put in a trusted+admin nodemap</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-504</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Lustre Operations Manual has a mention of a &quot;TrustedSystems&quot; nodemap, required for proper Lustre operation when the nodemap feature is activated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But it needs to be made clearer that this nodemap is really mandatory, and it should be also mentioned in the &quot;tutorial&quot; part in section 28.1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
